snippet.textDisplay:
It has 5 parts:
1. Fabulous sitar-esqe guitar piece by Ustad Tanveer Tafu in the beginning (00:14)
2. Jugal-bandi by Farid Ayaz and Abu Muhammad (01:15)
3. The actual Tarana sung in Raag Shahana (03:40)
4. The Dhamal part (06:18)
5. Final Jugal-bandi (10:26)


Part 2 and 3 overlapped once they started Tarana. Nevertheless each part and the whole arrangement is flawless and breathtaking.
